      "topic": "html",
      "sender": "Engineer",
      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>春节香瓜子葵花子促销页</title>\n<style>\n    :root {\n        --color-primary: #D32F2F;\n        --color-secondary: #FFD54F;\n        --color-light: #F4F4F5;\n        --color-dark: #B71C1C;\n    }\n    body {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif;\n        background-color: var(--color-light);\n        color: #333;\n        line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    header, section, footer, nav, aside, div {\n        padding: 20px;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n    .hero {\n        background-color: var(--color-primary);\n        color: white;\n        text-align: center;\n        padding: 60px 20px;\n    }\n    .hero h1 {\n        margin: 0 0 15px;\n        font-size: 2.4rem;\n    }\n    .hero p {\n        font-size: 1.2rem;\n    }\n    .content-section {\n        background-color: white;\n        max-width: 1200px;\n        margin: 20px auto;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n    }\n    .content-section h2,\n    .content-section h3 {\n        margin-top: 0;\n        color: var(--color-dark);\n    }\n    .price-box {\n        background-color: var(--color-secondary);\n        padding: 20px;\n        text-align: center;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        margin: 20px 0;\n    }\n    .price-box h3 {\n        margin: 0 0 10px;\n        font-size: 1.8rem;\n        color: var(--color-dark);\n    }\n    .promotion-banner {\n        background-color: var(--color-primary);\n        color: white;\n        padding: 15px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    .purchase-channel {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: center;\n        background-color: white;\n        border: 1px solid #eee;\n        padding: 20px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    .cart-panel {\n        background-color: var(--color-light);\n        border: 1px solid #ddd;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n    .category-list {\n        background-color: white;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        padding: 20px;\n        border: 1px solid #eee;\n    }\n    .coupon-zone {\n        background-color: var(--color-secondary);\n        padding: 20px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    .reviews {\n        background-color: white;\n        padding: 20px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        border: 1px solid #eee;\n    }\n    footer.footer-info {\n        background-color: var(--color-dark);\n        color: white;\n        text-align: center;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n        .purchase-channel {\n            width: 100%;\n        }\n        .content-section {\n            margin: 10px;\n        }\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<section class=\"hero\">\n    <h1>春节香瓜子葵花子主标题及节庆氛围文案</h1>\n    <p>吸引注意力的促销口号或节日问候</p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"content-section product-details\">\n    <h2>产品规格与卖点标题</h2>\n    <p>详细产品描述与营养信息</p>\n</section>\n\n<div class=\"price-box\">\n    <h3>优惠价格显示</h3>\n    <p>原价与折扣说明</p>\n</div>\n\n<section class=\"promotion-banner\">\n    <h3>限时促销与库存提醒标题</h3>\n    <p>倒计时或剩余数量提示</p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"purchase-channel\">\n    <h3>购买入口标题</h3>\n    <p>数量选择与加入购物车按钮描述</p>\n</section>\n\n<aside class=\"cart-panel\">\n    <h3>购物车标题</h3>\n    <p>已加购商品列表及数量调整描述</p>\n</aside>\n\n<nav class=\"category-list\">\n    <h3>春节零食分类标题</h3>\n    <p>相关商品发现提示</p>\n</nav>\n\n<section class=\"coupon-zone\">\n    <h3>优惠券领取标题</h3>\n    <p>优惠券使用说明及吸引参与文案</p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"reviews\">\n    <h3>用户评价标题</h3>\n    <p>精选评价与晒图描述</p>\n</section>\n\n<footer class=\"footer-info\">\n    <h3>品牌信息标题</h3>\n    <p>客服联系方式与售后说明</p>\n</footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
    }
